    Scope and Contents
Unit was established to improve the teaching/learning process at SSU, by emphasizing the development of the university's human resources.  The members of the Instructional Development Unit (IDU) were: Mary Jo Detweiler, John Wilshusen and Howard Dillon. This file contains memoranda, reports, meeting minutes, surveys and proposals.  Reports include: Instructional Development at SSU and the History Competency Project.  The survey is a Needs Assessment for the planning of the IDU (1973).  Memoranda are from Ron Ettinger and Howard to library and SSU faculty.  
  
